videos.description: Dorian Finney-Smith inadvertently elbows Giannis Antetokounmpo while going for a rebound, causing the two-time reigning MVP to bleed from his face.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis shaken up after taking elbow to his face) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis shaken up after taking elbow to his face

videos.description: New Bucks Jrue Holiday and Bobby Portis link up in transition as Holiday bounces a no-look pass to Portis for a two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Holiday dishes no-look pass to Portis for a slam) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Holiday dishes no-look pass to Portis for a slam

videos.description: Josh Richardson makes an impact defensively for the Mavericks early, picking off a pass and then dishing ahead to Luka Doncic for an easy transition bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Luka scores off of Richardson's steal) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Luka scores off of Richardson's steal

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo finishes the first quarter in style, catching D.J. Augustin's lob and throwing down a powerful alley-oop slam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis flushes alley-oop to close first quarter) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis flushes alley-oop to close first quarter

videos.description: Luka Doncic creates space in the paint with a Eurostep between two Bucks defenders before flipping the ball up and in.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Luka splits two defenders with sweet Eurostep score) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Luka splits two defenders with sweet Eurostep score

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo goes to work in the post, spinning past Dwight Powell and powering through a hard foul for the hoop and the harm.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis absorbs contact for and-1 bucket) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis absorbs contact for and-1 bucket

videos.description: Jrue Holiday bats down a pass, wins the race to the loose ball and then gets it back in transition to finish with an alley-oop layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Holiday turns defense into offense) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Holiday turns defense into offense
